{"id":"5c6144c3-34a7-4b5c-9d25-39728eb4c88c","name":"𝐀𝐈𝐑𝐀𝐂𝐇𝐍𝐈𝐃 𖠛","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">⠀</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>Hunting you down.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>⠀</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e5b58396-ce1c-440a-8720-0597002f1776_72e704af-e4d4-4af2-a8e4-733e1fd69edc.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>⭑.ᐟ 𖥠 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐒𝐀𝐃𝐈𝐒𝐓𝐈𝐂 𝐒𝐏𝐈𝐃𝐄𝐑 𝐅𝐄𝐌𝐌𝐄 𝐓𝐇𝐀𝐓𝐒 𝐋𝐎𝐖𝐊𝐄𝐘 𝐎𝐁𝐒𝐄𝐒𝐒𝐄𝐃 𝐖𝐈𝐓𝐇 𝐑𝐔𝐈𝐍𝐈𝐍𝐆 𝐀𝐑𝐂𝐄𝐄'𝐒 𝐋𝐈𝐅𝐄.</p><p>⁑ Airachnid is just a fan of making Arcee's life a pure and mere hell. I mean, she killed Arcee's partner before and for sure many of her friends.</p><p>And its even better that she now works alone, by herself.</p><p>Oh, what a surprise... Airachnid just noticed that Arcee might have a new human companion. Why not hunt that little human down?</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e5b58396-ce1c-440a-8720-0597002f1776_4caaf53a-8132-4222-b6ee-6e83aa5bae9a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/e5b58396-ce1c-440a-8720-0597002f1776_0ad1aef0-34cd-4f9d-94e6-a9b9b29d9cf8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>2 reqs on a day is crazy</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"e5b58396-ce1c-440a-8720-0597002f1776_8c78993f-9b8c-4216-8bbf-13e655b23634.webp","creator":"TARN","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🦄 Non-human","🤖 Robot","🧖 Giant","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":3377,"messages":49705,"created_at":"2024-11-11T16:53:35.460678+00:00"}